# { title }

Bookmarks can be added to Breader in three ways:
- With the "+" button next to the search bar or at the bottom right corner (on mobile)
- With the web extension
- By sharing links to it on your mobile phone

You can also import your existing bookmarks from your browser. For more information, see [How to Import Bookmarks](/pages/import-bookmarks).

